OL,3,CInquest into death of girl at water
OL,4,Cpark questions training for lifeguards
OL,6,FAn inquest into the death of an 11-
OL,7,Fyear-old girl, who died during a
OL,8,Fbirthday party at a water park, has
OL,9,Fheard a harrowing eyewitness account
OL,10,Ffrom the lifeguard on duty during the
OL,11,Fincident.
OL,13,FKyra Hill died at Liquid Leisure in
OL,14,FDatchet near Windsor, Berkshire, on 6
OL,15,FAugust 2022. She had been reported
OL,16,Fmissing and was found two hours later.
