OL,3,CInquest into death of girl at water
OL,4,Cpark questions training for lifeguards
OL,6,FHer family arrived at Reading
OL,7,FCoroner's Court for the inquest today
OL,8,F(13 May 2025). Her father had
OL,9,Fpreviously vowed to uncover "the whole
OL,10,Ftruth" over her death.
OL,12,FThe Senior Berkshire Coroner, Heidi
OL,13,FConner, warned Kyra's family that the
OL,14,Finquest was going to be difficult.
OL,16,FA judge previously fined Liquid
OL,17,FLeisure Windsor #80,000 and ordered
OL,18,Fthem to pay #30,000 costs.
