OL,3,CInquest into death of girl at water
OL,4,Cpark questions training for lifeguards
OL,6,FThe lifeguard on duty was 17 at the
OL,7,Ftime and was referred to in court as
OL,8,F'Abbi'. She had qualified in life-
OL,9,Fsaving, four months before the
OL,10,Fincident.
OL,12,FShe said she was not trained in
OL,13,Funderwater rescue, just surface
OL,14,Frescue. When Kyra went missing, Abbi
OL,15,Fsaw splashing in the water and said
OL,16,Fher gut instinct was that someone had
OL,17,Fgone under.
