OL,3,CInquest into death of girl at water
OL,4,Cpark questions training for lifeguards
OL,6,FMembers of the public told her someone
OL,7,Fhad got out of the water, but she said
OL,8,Fshe was unconvinced and called for
OL,9,Fhelp.
OL,11,FA search was launched for a missing
OL,12,Fchild around the park, but she
OL,13,Fpersisted and dove three times to see
OL,14,Fif she could find anyone, but she said
OL,15,Fvisibility was terrible.
OL,17,FShe heard someone say, "where's Kyra?"
OL,18,Fand so was convinced what she had seen
OL,19,Fwas someone in distress.
