OL,3,CInquest into death of girl at water
OL,4,Cpark questions training for lifeguards
OL,6,FAdults were also not informed about
OL,7,Fthe need for adult supervision or that
OL,8,Ftheir child needed to be a competent
OL,9,Fswimmer for such conditions.
OL,11,FThe inquest heard that Kyra went under
OL,12,Fwhere the depth was 2.6 metres. These
OL,13,Ffacts were not detailed in the risk
OL,14,Fassessment for the area known as "The
OL,15,FBeach" where she died.
OL,17,FThe inquest was also told that
OL,18,Falthough the bottom of the edge of the
OL,19,Fwater was sand-covered, as the water
OL,20,Fgot deeper the bottom became silt and
OL,21,Fsoft mud.
