OL,3,CInquest into death of girl at water
OL,4,Cpark questions training for lifeguards
OL,6,FGiving evidence for Liquid Leisure,
OL,7,FMr. Marston said there should have
OL,8,Fbeen more than one lifeguard on duty
OL,9,Ffor the number of people in the water,
OL,10,Fsaid to be around 42, at the time Kyra
OL,11,Fwent missing.
OL,13,FToday was about determining the facts
OL,14,Faround how Kyra died, not about
OL,15,Fapportioning blame, the Coroner said.
OL,17,FThe inquest continues.
